# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TEAM DEFINITIONS
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# @biometrics-core - Core development team (default reviewers)
# @biometrics-go - Go backend developers
# @biometrics-frontend - Frontend/TypeScript developers
# @biometrics-docs - Documentation writers and maintainers
# @biometrics-devops - DevOps and infrastructure team
# @biometrics-design - Design and assets team
# @biometrics-architecture - System architects
# @biometrics-data - Data engineers and DBAs
# @biometrics-ai - AI/ML engineers
# @biometrics-product - Product managers
# @go-reviewers - Go code reviewers (senior Go developers)
#
# Note: Team definitions must be created in GitHub Organization Settings
# URL: https://github.com/organizations/BIOMETRICS/settings/teams
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

